# üì¶ Project Template -- React + Go REST API + MySQL (with Todo Table)

This project is a full-stack template consisting of:

-   **Frontend:** React (Vite)
-   **Backend:** Go REST API
-   **Database:** MySQL
-   **Includes a Todo table**

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## üìÅ Folder Structure

    /project-root
     ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ /Web            # React (Vite) frontend
     ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ /server         # Go backend (REST API)
     ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ README.md
     ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ .env            # Environment variables

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ‚öôÔ∏è Environment Variables

### Backend (.env in /server or project root)

    # Database / Server configuration
    DB_USER=            # Your database username
    DB_PASSWORD=        # Your database password
    DB_HOST=localhost   # Database host (default: localhost)
    DB_PORT=3306        # Database port
    DB_NAME=            # Your database name

    Server_PORT=3000    # Server port (default: 3000)

    # Website configuration
    VITE_Server_IP=http://localhost  # Server host
    VITE_Server_PORT=3000            # Server port
    VITE_Web_PORT=5000               # Web port

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## üóÑÔ∏è Database Setup

Create the database:

    CREATE DATABASE <db_name>;
    USE <db_name>;

### üìå Create Todo Table

    CREATE TABLE todos (
        id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
        task VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
        completed TINYINT(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
    );

The table stores:

-   **id:** Primary key\
-   **title:** Todo title\
-   **description:** Optional description\
-   **completed:** Whether the todo is finished\
-   **created_at:** Creation date

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ‚ñ∂Ô∏è Running the Project

### Backend (Go)

    cd server
    go mod tidy
    go run main.go

Backend runs at: `http://localhost:3000`

### Frontend (React)

    cd web
    pnpm install
    pnpm run dev

Frontend runs at: `http://localhost:5000`

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## üîå API Structure (Todo Example)

    GET    /api/todos
    GET    /api/todos/:id
    POST   /api/todos
    PUT    /api/todos/:id
    DELETE /api/todos/:id

**POST Body Example:**

    {
      "title": "Buy milk",
      "description": "Remember lactose-free",
      "completed": false
    }

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## üõ†Ô∏è Building

### Backend

    cd server
    go build -o server

### Frontend

    cd web
    pnpm run build

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ‚ùì Troubleshooting

  Problem                  Solution
  ------------------------ --------------------------------------------
  No DB connection         Check username and password in `.env`
  Backend not responding   Check Server_PORT and ensure Go is running
  Frontend CORS errors     Check CORS configuration in Go API
  Port already in use      Change port in `.env`
